title: VA spiritual worlds (yellow sunshine explosion)
description:
VARIOUS ARTISTS - SPIRITUAL WORLDS 
-Music For The Mystical Mind-ethno chill out & shamanic beats 

YSE RECORDINGS will surprise the market with a brand new Chill- Out Concept exploring the depth of the minds! SPRITUAL WORLDS contains mystical chill out anthems, music with healing power and intense impact on your mind and your soul. SPIRITULA WORLDS is not your usual "chill out" collection! SPRITUAL WORLDS combines modern electronic music with the Spirit of ancient folks and mystical tribes. SPIRUTAL WORLDS is an intense journey, which takes you out of this world into the tomorrow..explore yourselves with the magic sound of Ethno- Vocals, Celtic soundscapes, Shamanic beats and invisible spirits crawling through your stereo...SPIRITUAL WORLDS is a true listening experience and features carefully selected acts such as JUNO REACTOR, TOTAL ECLIPSE, SPHONGLE, EPHEMERAL MISTS, DIGITAL MYSTERY TOUR, CELTIC CROSS, UNIVERSAL SOUND, MANMADEMAN pls. many more!!
